search_results.title: Momo (novel)
search_results.snippet: Momo, also known as The Grey Gentlemen or The Men in Grey, is a fantasy novel by Michael Ende, published in 1973. It is about the concept of time.

search_results.title: Meet Momo! Children's Books Author Site for Arline Gray
search_results.snippet: Momo's adventures are written by his human mom, Arline Gray. Arline taught second grade for thirty-five years in Avon Lake, Ohio and loved every minute of it!
